<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Plan Assigned</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF9933 0%, #138808 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .announcement {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e8 0%, #fff3e0 100%);
            border: 2px solid #FF9933;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .announcement h2 {
            color: #138808;
            font-size: 26px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .announcement p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .plan-details {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #f8f9fa 100%);
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .plan-details h3 {
            color: #FF9933;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .plan-info {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .info-item {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 250px;
        }
        
        .info-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #138808;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .info-value {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 5px;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border-left: 4px solid #FF9933;
        }
        
        .benefits-section {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .benefits-section h3 {
            color: #138808;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .benefits-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .benefit-item {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #138808;
        }
        
        .benefit-item h4 {
            color: #FF9933;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .benefit-item p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .important-notice {
            background-color: #d1ecf1;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .important-notice h4 {
            color: #0c5460;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .important-notice p {
            color: #0c5460;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .action-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF9933 0%, #138808 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .plan-info {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            .benefits-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Indians in Ghana</h1>
            <p>Membership Management</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="announcement">
                <h2>üéâ New Plan Assigned!</h2>
                <p>Congratulations {{firstName}}! You've been assigned a new membership plan.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="plan-details">
                <h3>Your New Plan Details</h3>
                
                <div class="plan-info">
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="info-label">Plan Name</div>
                        <div class="info-value">{{planName}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="info-label">Plan Type</div>
                        <div class="info-value">{{planType}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="plan-info">
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="info-label">Effective From</div>
                        <div class="info-value">{{effectiveDate}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="info-label">Valid Until</div>
                        <div class="info-value">{{expiryDate}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                {{#if maxDeals}}
                <div class="plan-info">
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="info-label">Monthly Deal Limit</div>
                        <div class="info-value">{{maxDeals}} deals</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="info-label">Redemption Limit</div>
                        <div class="info-value">{{maxRedemptions}} per month</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="benefits-section">
                <h3>What's Included in Your {{planName}} Plan</h3>
                
                <div class="benefits-grid">
                    {{#if isUserPlan}}
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <h4>‚ú® Exclusive Deals</h4>
                        <p>Access to special discounts and offers from Indian businesses</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <h4>üé´ Deal Redemptions</h4>
                        <p>Redeem up to {{maxRedemptions}} deals per month</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <h4>üèÜ Priority Support</h4>
                        <p>Get faster customer support and assistance</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <h4>üì± Digital Membership</h4>
                        <p>Digital membership card with QR code verification</p>
                    </div>
                    {{else}}
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <h4>üè™ Deal Posting</h4>
                        <p>Post up to {{maxDeals}} deals per month</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <h4>üìä Business Analytics</h4>
                        <p>Track your deal performance and customer engagement</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <h4>üéØ Targeted Reach</h4>
                        <p>Reach the Indian community with your offerings</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <h4>üíº Business Profile</h4>
                        <p>Enhanced business listing with premium features</p>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="important-notice">
                <h4>üìã Important Information:</h4>
                <p>
                    {{#if assignedBy}}
                    This plan was assigned by {{assignedBy}} on {{assignmentDate}}.
                    {{else}}
                    This plan assignment is effective immediately.
                    {{/if}}
                    {{#if planMessage}}
                    <br><br><strong>Message:</strong> {{planMessage}}
                    {{/if}}
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="action-section">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="btn">Access Your Dashboard</a>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0;">
                <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 15px;"><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
                <ul style="color: #666; padding-left: 20px;">
                    {{#if isUserPlan}}
                    <li>Log into your account to see your new plan benefits</li>
                    <li>Browse available deals from Indian businesses</li>
                    <li>Start redeeming deals with your increased monthly limit</li>
                    <li>Connect with other community members</li>
                    {{else}}
                    <li>Log into your merchant dashboard to see your new plan</li>
                    <li>Start posting deals with your new monthly allowance</li>
                    <li>Monitor your business analytics and performance</li>
                    <li>Engage with the Indian community customers</li>
                    {{/if}}
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Indians in Ghana</strong> - Connecting Community, Creating Value</p>
            <p>This is an automated security notification. Please do not reply to this message.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions about your new plan, please contact our support team.</p>
            <p>Email: {{supportEmail}} | Website: www.indiansinghana.com</p>
            
            <div style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
                <p>{{fullName}}</p>
                <p>This email was sent to {{email}}</p>
                <p>Plan Assignment Date: {{assignmentDate}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
